MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 1 :  Reduces the cost of building Floor structures by 20%.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 1 :  Reduces the cost of building Floor structures by 20%.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 2 : Increases the chance to double-craft traps based on Outlander Lab Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 2 : Increases the chance to double-craft traps based on Outlander Lab Rating.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 3 : Increases damage dealt by traps based on Outlander Lab Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 3 : Increases damage dealt by traps based on Outlander Lab Rating.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 4 : Increases the move speed granted while on Player-Built floors by 10%.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 4 : Increases the move speed granted while on Player-Built floors by 10%.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 5 : Diamonds in the Rough : Improves all three Explorer Fragments.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 5 : Diamonds in the Rough : Improves all three Explorer Fragments.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: -Offensive Fragment : Increases the lifespan of T.E.D.D.Y. to 30 seconds.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: -Offensive Fragment : Increases the lifespan of T.E.D.D.Y. to 30 seconds.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: -Defensive Fragment : Increases the bonus Shield added to 200% of maximum shield.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: -Defensive Fragment : Increases the bonus Shield added to 200% of maximum shield.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: -Specialty Fragment : Increases yield of resources by 25%. Allows for rare crystal drops.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: -Specialty Fragment : Increases yield of resources by 25%. Allows for rare crystal drops.
